In the INTEREST OF G.R., Minor Child, G.R., Minor Child, Appellant. No. 18-1644 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 1, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A minor child appeals the juvenile court decision finding he committed the delinquent act of sexual abuse in the second degree. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
